{
  "stem": "628.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And what was going on with your education at the time?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Education, there was none.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Jewish schools were closed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I walked-- the last two years of still staying in Germany, nothing much.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I played about.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I walked about everywhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, I waked the streets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's why I saw Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's why I saw Hitler-- I walked the streets.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I saw the SS.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I still went to-- there us some-- not schools, but kinderheims, you know, Augustas, I went there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But nothing happened there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was the Jewish school also in Alexanderplatz, but the-- the teachers were not really giving a proper, what's it called, the schooling, because they-- then-- then they burned the schools, you know?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It happened then in the synagogues, that was also at the same time as Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They burned that all, and you couldn't go to school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One and a half years of my life in Berlin, I didn't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My sister continued to work for Siemens, again, a goy-- a non-Jewish family, until-- until the day came, '43.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the first-- and it must be have been already in beginning '43, that suddenly, on the door, [GERMAN]. 4 o' clock in the morning, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And shouting, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And two Gestapo came in, in their leather coats, like they're known.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All you have to leave behind, just hand luggage, and downstairs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Downstairs, my sister was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My sister went mad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Not one neighbor in the house, three floors up, coming down, came out and looked.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We said, oh, we didn't see any neighbors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I remember that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We came out the house, the street was suddenly gone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Nobody was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In the windows, nobody was looking out of the windows.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
